        <updateDate>2007-10-27T14:45:30Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Wayne &quot;Cotton&quot; Morgan Bulletproof Vest Act of 2007 - Amends the Omnibus Crime Control and Safe Streets Act of 1968 to waive the grantee matching funds requirement applicable to the grant program for purchasing bulletproof armor vests to the extent that such vests are purchased for law enforcement officers who work in high security risk areas and correctional officers who transport prisoners.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
